Package net.firstpartners.ui

Class RedGui

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.event.WindowAdapter
      • net.firstpartners.ui.RedGui
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.event.WindowFocusListener, java.awt.event.WindowListener, java.awt.event.WindowStateListener, java.lang.Runnable, java.util.EventListener, IGiveFeedbackToUsers, ILogger
    public class RedGui
extends java.awt.event.WindowAdapter
implements java.awt.event.WindowListener, java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.lang.Runnable, ILogger, IGiveFeedbackToUsers
    Desktop GUI for Red Piranha Desktop User interface to ease calling of Rules / running the webserver needed for the office plugin. This is just a facade, called by RedCommandLine (unless the user has configured it not to)
    Author:
    PBrowne
